# Body Particle System

## Overview
The **Body Particle System** is an interactive visualization tool that integrates body pose detection with dynamic particle effects. Using Mediapipe for body pose detection, this system overlays particle effects on body parts in real-time, providing a visually engaging experience for creative coding, installations, or educational purposes.

---

## Features
- **Real-Time Pose Detection**: Leverages Mediapipe to detect body landmarks.
- **Dynamic Particle Effects**: Generates particles that react to body movements.


---

